WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.088 --> 00:00:05.440
Welcome and good evening, everybody.

00:00:05.440 --> 00:00:11.107
I know it's late, so let's go over what the Lord showed us yesterday.

00:00:11.107 --> 00:00:15.072
Yesterday was heavy; we were in the Spirit.

00:00:19.060 --> 00:00:22.440
I saw the boils on the people, and they were massive—the size of half-dollars.

00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:28.930
Some of them were the size of quarters, and some like dimes.

00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:35.840
There were boils on all their skin, and they looked like they were filled with some kind of fluid.

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:43.960
It looked almost like the membrane when you touch a stove and get a burn on your hand, like a blister.

00:00:43.960 --> 00:00:50.707
That's what this looked like on the people I saw in New York.

00:00:55.274 --> 00:00:59.542
What I thought was interesting was that it was on their mouths, in their mouths, and on their throats.

00:01:02.785 --> 00:01:08.711
In the vision, I went inside the body and could see that it was on their physical throat and inside.

00:01:14.191 --> 00:01:18.520
Then I saw a blackout.

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:22.255
I kept hearing 'darkness,' and it was cold.

00:01:24.530 --> 00:01:34.742
I could see the buildings in New York in this vision, and all the buildings were blacked out with no power on.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:46.000
As there was no power, I saw people with 50-gallon drums, putting fires in them to keep warm.

00:01:46.271 --> 00:01:56.880
They had scarves and hats on—the kind that pull over your ears—and they had these coats on, keeping themselves warm by these 50-gallon drums.

00:01:57.116 --> 00:02:08.800
I was praying into that, but then I saw people in the background with buildings on fire, and they were looting what they could.

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:22.080
As I panned out through the lens, I could see Toronto, and it spread from Toronto all the way down to Miami.

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:29.040
Sorry, I was around some mold today and I'm coughing a little bit, but all is well.

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:32.171
I've got this; it's not a virus, it's because of the mold.

00:02:32.171 --> 00:02:32.617
I hate mold.

00:02:36.112 --> 00:02:48.390
I saw it go all the way down the East Coast, and as I saw this, I saw mass migration again; people were leaving.

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:59.640
I saw a massive white medical ship with a huge red cross on it parked outside of New York.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:11.577
The hospitals were full, and they were transporting people by helicopter and other ways to this big boat.

00:03:12.411 --> 00:03:32.335
The ship was docked, but people were being transported to it, which I thought was interesting because you only take a helicopter ride if it's very serious and you're not about to make it.

00:03:34.025 --> 00:03:37.640
They don't give you a helicopter ride just to give you a helicopter ride.

00:03:39.063 --> 00:03:45.480
The other part was I saw a mime.

00:03:45.480 --> 00:04:03.020
I saw a white-faced clown with blackest mascara around his eyes and teardrops—the small part of a teardrop that would drop on your cheek, kind of like what gang members do.

00:04:05.903 --> 00:04:18.565
This was a massive teardrop that started at the top and went down like this; it had a black liner and white in the middle, and his eyes were blacked out.

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:25.040
This was on both eyes.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:47.686
He was wearing a black and white outfit with a hat like Laurel and Hardy wear; it was a circle with a little dome, a white band around it, and a flower coming off the side.

00:04:50.788 --> 00:04:59.920
He was making a bent-over motion and was crying without sound—a mime.

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:06.267
He looked like he was sobbing and making a noise, but with no sound.

00:05:07.467 --> 00:05:10.720
If you were to put noise to it, it would be a travail cry.

00:05:13.583 --> 00:05:16.560
I know that was symbolic; there's something to this.

00:05:16.891 --> 00:05:21.160
Not everything is black and white; it's a metaphor.

00:05:40.433 --> 00:05:40.800
That's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:42.783
Then I saw dogwood trees and I heard 'dogwood, dogwood.

00:05:42.783 --> 00:05:45.920
' I knew it was symbolic of something else.

00:06:01.726 --> 00:06:02.023
A lot of you are researchers, and you say, Brandon, that Jesus was crucified on a dogwood tree.

00:06:03.263 --> 00:06:10.490
I don't know how people know that unless it says it in the Word and I'm just ignorant of it, but it was interesting.

00:06:10.490 --> 00:06:11.680
I saw dogwood blossoms.

00:06:11.680 --> 00:06:15.755
I knew the Lord, when I heard the Father say 'dogwood' and 'lamb's quarters, lamb's quarters.

00:06:15.755 --> 00:06:22.440
' I saw a little white flower and I saw the lamb.

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:25.840
Then I went in the Spirit to Ireland.

00:06:25.840 --> 00:06:27.622
The Lord said, 'Look at Ireland.

00:06:27.622 --> 00:06:34.053
' So I was looking at Ireland and thinking, 'What are you trying to say about this?

00:06:34.053 --> 00:06:45.726
' A lot of people sent Diana and me emails saying dogwood and lamb's quarters are for your intestines and parasites.

00:06:46.514 --> 00:06:48.103
The bark helps your stomach problems.

00:06:48.103 --> 00:06:51.200
There are medicinal purposes for these lamb's quarters.

00:06:57.420 --> 00:06:57.785
I thought that was interesting.

00:06:57.785 --> 00:07:05.150
Praying into that, why is the Lord talking about this?

00:07:18.080 --> 00:07:19.236
He said, 'Don't take it.

00:07:19.236 --> 00:07:25.110
' The Lord kept saying, 'Don't take it.

00:07:46.509 --> 00:07:47.126
Don't take it.

00:07:47.126 --> 00:07:47.309
Don't take it.

00:07:47.309 --> 00:07:49.120
' So I said, 'Don't take what?

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:53.809
' I saw a vial again.

00:07:53.809 --> 00:07:56.200
Then somebody gave me Revelation 19.

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:58.593
Son, could you pull that up?

00:08:14.046 --> 00:08:14.337
I believe it was Revelation 19.

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:19.760
It said the boils come on the people.

00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:30.871
If mama were here—she's busy—but the scripture talks about in Revelation the boils coming on the people after they take the mark.

00:08:30.871 --> 00:08:37.461
Maybe, just me speaking into it, I was having a vision of the Tribulation again.

00:08:45.528 --> 00:08:54.350
I think it's interesting as we're praying because the Lord kept saying, 'Don't take it.

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:58.600
' Well, don't take what?

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:08.760
The mark?

00:09:08.760 --> 00:09:10.760
Was it the mark?

00:09:10.760 --> 00:09:28.575
I don't add to or take away from anything, but I think it's interesting because, lately, the things the Lord is showing us—He talked about Mystery Babylon and the major shakings that are coming.

00:09:28.575 --> 00:09:37.280
I believe the closer we get to the Tribulation, the more the Lord is letting us see into it to pray.

00:09:37.280 --> 00:09:50.080
Regardless, I want to say this: God wishes that none should perish but all come to repentance—all of us, even the people who are going through the Tribulation.

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:53.320
There's always a way of escaping every area of our life.

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:59.145
Even to the point of praying for our brothers and sisters who get left—the unbelievers in the Tribulation.

00:09:59.145 --> 00:10:01.920
Could we be interceding for them?

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:07.740
I don't doubt it; I believe that's how merciful God is.

00:10:07.740 --> 00:10:12.827
But are we getting that close to it?

00:10:12.827 --> 00:10:15.154
I'm telling you, Jesus Christ is coming.

00:10:18.447 --> 00:10:20.950
You must know Him as your Lord and personal Savior.

00:10:20.950 --> 00:10:22.971
You're running out of time.

00:10:32.535 --> 00:10:32.750
The urgency of the hour—it's time for the Body of Christ to wake up.

00:10:32.750 --> 00:10:33.610
Jesus is coming.

00:10:33.610 --> 00:10:44.752
Many of you are asleep; many are not awake for what's about to happen on this earth.

00:10:57.796 --> 00:10:58.071
The signs of the times are about to heighten, doubling and tripling.

00:10:58.071 --> 00:11:03.035
It's like the Lord showing me anointing on ministries; they're doubling and tripling.

00:11:03.035 --> 00:11:18.430
If you just spend time with the Father and seek Him daily—not just whenever it's convenient—finding that intimacy, going back to the first love, going back to what you fell in love with, that tugging at your heart.

00:11:18.430 --> 00:11:20.530
'Oh, Father, how are you today?

00:11:26.160 --> 00:11:26.740
I want to know You more.

00:11:42.390 --> 00:11:42.755
I want to fall more in love with the Lord.

00:11:42.755 --> 00:11:45.649
Please, God, create in me a clean heart.

00:11:45.649 --> 00:11:52.040
' Stripping all this stuff off of me that would be ungodly before You.

00:11:52.040 --> 00:11:56.820
What is holding me back from coming to the greater glory?

00:11:56.820 --> 00:12:02.450
What is it inside of me that You see, Lord, that is repulsive to You?

00:12:02.450 --> 00:12:13.549
To be on that potter's wheel and be molded and made every day, staying from glory to glory to cultivate and accelerate.

00:12:15.120 --> 00:12:17.160
The Lord keeps talking to me about 2026.

00:12:17.160 --> 00:12:22.650
And even, you know, just bringing about the alien stuff.

00:12:22.650 --> 00:12:26.325
I am telling you, ladies and gentlemen, great fearful sights you will see that will bring you to your knees.

00:12:26.325 --> 00:12:33.994
We are about to have great deception beyond anybody's comprehension for what we are about to see.

00:12:43.956 --> 00:12:44.173
It is the plan of the enemy.

00:12:44.173 --> 00:13:03.799
One of the major things Jesus told me when I went to heaven and I was on the edge of it, he said to me, "Brandon, right before I come, one of the major things you will see in this earth is that they will talk about aliens a lot.

00:13:03.799 --> 00:13:10.344
" This was in a visitation I had on July 6th of 2014.

00:13:10.344 --> 00:13:18.490
The Lord said to me, "There will be many on the news all the time talking about aliens, ships, and things like that.

00:13:18.490 --> 00:13:25.912
" I heard somebody say that Rick Renner was talking about the aliens in the water and the Nephilim.

00:13:25.912 --> 00:13:34.015
Ladies and gentlemen, it is about desensitizing you to what is about to happen.

00:13:41.948 --> 00:13:46.710
The main thing the Antichrist will say when he comes on the scene—when I told you he comes before, he stands in an Oval Office area with a red carpet behind him.

00:13:46.710 --> 00:13:56.620
Does anybody remember me saying he stands in a red carpet area with all these lights and the stage, and he tells the Christians they were taken because of rebellion?

00:13:56.620 --> 00:14:06.453
Now, I have my own family members; some of them say they don't even believe in the rapture of the church.

00:14:06.453 --> 00:14:13.954
They don't believe any of this stuff; they think we are all drinking bad Kool-Aid.

00:14:14.726 --> 00:14:19.235
I am trying to tell you all, we are not appointed unto wrath.

00:14:31.513 --> 00:14:32.040
Jesus Christ is not a wife beater.

00:14:32.040 --> 00:14:40.950
There is nothing you can say to convince me that we are going to walk through the tribulation.

00:14:40.950 --> 00:14:51.303
Most of it is like the people who think God is going to knock the snot out of his kids that he loves.

00:14:51.303 --> 00:14:53.670
He is not God.

00:14:53.680 --> 00:15:06.446
If we being evil give good gifts to our children, how much more does the heavenly Father give good gifts to those that love him?

00:15:06.446 --> 00:15:08.410
That is, I believe, Matthew 7.

00:15:08.410 --> 00:15:11.940
I want to encourage you all today.

00:15:11.940 --> 00:15:15.947
God is not a wife beater.

00:15:15.947 --> 00:15:19.074
God is not beating his bride.

00:15:22.085 --> 00:15:27.371
He is not up there going, "Let's punish you; let you go through some hell because you need to.

00:15:28.143 --> 00:15:30.920
" That is not our God.

00:15:30.920 --> 00:15:36.533
God is a rewarder of those who diligently seek him, love him, and follow him.

00:15:36.533 --> 00:15:45.320
So, I just want to encourage you all today to get off the tribulation train.

00:15:47.876 --> 00:15:48.747
I don't believe it.

00:15:48.747 --> 00:16:00.320
Everything I have seen, when I went to the tribulation, the ones that were left were like the five virgins that didn't have their lamps full of oil.

00:16:13.260 --> 00:16:13.430
It was not the ones that were full of oil.

00:16:13.430 --> 00:16:16.549
There were ten; five were ready, five were not.

00:16:16.549 --> 00:16:18.142
Which one are you?

00:16:18.142 --> 00:16:26.100
Is your lamp full of oil, or are you one that is empty, saying, "You know what?

00:16:30.936 --> 00:16:31.152
I like living in the world.

00:16:31.368 --> 00:16:41.815
I like partying, I like having premarital sex, I like going out and looking at bad things on the internet, I like going to the strip club or drinking or whatever.

00:16:41.815 --> 00:16:44.160
" Are you sold out to Jesus?

00:16:44.160 --> 00:16:51.759
It is time to get real and be sold out to Jesus, to be all-in.

00:16:51.759 --> 00:17:04.984
I say it over and over again on this channel, but I have that urgency again tonight to warn you: we are running out of time.

00:17:04.984 --> 00:17:10.290
Unless a man is born again, he cannot enter the kingdom of God.

00:17:10.290 --> 00:17:10.765
Who is influencing you?

00:17:10.765 --> 00:17:14.079
What is pulling you away from it?

00:17:14.079 --> 00:17:15.360
Cut it off.

00:17:15.360 --> 00:17:24.740
What speaks louder in your life that is against the Word and against the Father coming up higher?

00:17:24.740 --> 00:17:27.400
Cut it out of your life.

00:17:42.120 --> 00:17:42.427
It is a cancer.

00:17:42.427 --> 00:17:43.653
Only seek Jesus.

00:17:43.653 --> 00:17:44.880
It is time.

00:17:50.587 --> 00:17:56.790
The Lord tells me, "Brandon, you must tell them and shake them out of their slumber all the time.

00:18:09.880 --> 00:18:10.140
" He warns me, "Tell them I am coming, Brandon.

00:18:10.140 --> 00:18:12.444
Tell them there is no time.

00:18:12.444 --> 00:18:14.440
" You say, "What does that mean to you, Brandon?

00:18:14.440 --> 00:18:18.520
" Even if it is five years, folks, on the scale of eternity, that is nothing.

00:18:18.520 --> 00:18:24.040
It is grace if he gives us five more years.

00:18:24.040 --> 00:18:26.851
It is grace if he gives us ten.

00:18:26.851 --> 00:18:30.553
I don't see it any more than that.

00:18:30.553 --> 00:18:38.450
I am believing for the next three years during Trump's term, during the next cycle.

00:18:38.450 --> 00:18:44.540
But I still see right now praying for JD Vance in 2028, and I have seen clearly into 2032.

00:18:51.495 --> 00:18:51.720
But no man knows the day or the hour.

00:18:54.280 --> 00:18:59.285
We know the signs of the times as we watch the fig tree.

00:19:00.194 --> 00:19:05.440
So I want to encourage you today to keep your lamp full.

00:19:05.440 --> 00:19:07.919
He could come back tomorrow.

00:19:07.919 --> 00:19:16.360
I believe he will come on Rosh Hashanah.

00:19:16.360 --> 00:19:21.040
I believe that is the timeframe he will come in, the September timeframe.

00:19:21.040 --> 00:19:30.218
Everybody expected it back on September 23rd, and I warned you over and over again, they were missing it.

00:19:30.218 --> 00:19:33.679
That was the point of no return.

00:19:33.679 --> 00:19:39.200
He said, "You have entered into the point of no return of September 2025, the 23rd.

00:19:39.200 --> 00:19:46.511
" He said that was the point of no return as labor pains upon a woman.

00:19:46.511 --> 00:19:47.956
Where are we in the labor pains?

00:19:47.956 --> 00:19:52.034
He said, "Brandon, you are at the point of no time for an epidural.

00:19:52.034 --> 00:20:04.074
" So you ladies that have had a baby recently, you know there is a point in time where there is no more time for an epidural, and that is where we are.

00:20:08.951 --> 00:20:09.240
It is about time to push.

00:20:10.128 --> 00:20:11.383
You have dilated to a ten; it is time to push.

00:20:11.383 --> 00:20:13.160
That is where we are in these end times.

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:16.485
As of the 23rd of September, the point of no return.

00:20:16.485 --> 00:20:19.405
What does that mean to you?

00:20:19.405 --> 00:20:23.448
Well, the Lord said this is the time.

00:20:29.128 --> 00:20:31.291
It is the time that he said, "I am not out of mercy, I am out of time.

00:20:31.291 --> 00:20:40.234
" We are at the point of push, and the greatest revival, the greatest end-time harvest of souls this world has ever known, is about to hit this planet.

00:20:47.551 --> 00:20:47.800
But he is calling all hands on deck.

00:20:47.800 --> 00:20:58.008
As we saw last night, Jesus was walking amongst the wheat, and the wheat was bowing down before him.

00:20:58.008 --> 00:21:04.755
He was feeling the wheat through his fingers and he was weighing it in his hands.

00:21:04.755 --> 00:21:11.950
He looked at me in the spirit and he said, "Brandon, the harvest is plentiful, son, and the laborers are few.

00:21:11.950 --> 00:21:13.160
Help me tonight.

00:21:13.160 --> 00:21:15.960
" We had 90 plus salvations.

00:21:15.960 --> 00:21:20.040
12 people in South Korea got born again.

00:21:20.040 --> 00:21:27.180
Buddhists came to Jesus last night, 12 of them, all to the glory of God.

00:21:27.180 --> 00:21:36.580
It is wonderful when 12 Buddhists give their hearts to Jesus Christ, people that did not know him at all.

00:21:39.824 --> 00:21:45.320
Over the last couple of days here, we have had well over 500 salvations.

00:21:45.320 --> 00:21:47.942
People know inside that something is up.

00:21:47.942 --> 00:21:50.689
There is an urgency of the hour.

00:21:50.689 --> 00:22:08.840
It is kind of like an animal that knows there is about to be a major earthquake or a tsunami; they always run for the hills because they sense danger is coming.

00:22:08.840 --> 00:22:18.345
There are many of you, they call it a sixth sense, whatever; I believe the Holy Ghost is inside of every single one of us, tugging at your heart.

00:22:28.007 --> 00:22:30.600
Even if you're not born again, he's at the door of your heart knocking; you're running out of time.

00:22:30.600 --> 00:22:39.742
So they come and they watch us and they pray with us because a lot of them want to know about crypto.

00:22:39.742 --> 00:22:45.616
A lot of people always ask me, "What are the five pillars, Brandon?

00:22:45.616 --> 00:22:47.212
" I'm not a financial adviser.

00:22:47.212 --> 00:22:52.773
I can tell you what I've seen in the spirit, but it's only what I feel the Holy Spirit has told me.

00:22:57.440 --> 00:23:01.040
And if it's off and it's wrong—and I'm flesh—you know what, we can miss it.

00:23:01.040 --> 00:23:09.190
I'm not telling you what to do with your money because you'd be going, "Brandon, you told me to do this.

00:23:09.190 --> 00:23:14.006
" I did not tell you to do anything; I told you to pray about it.

00:23:14.006 --> 00:23:18.360
I am human and I can miss it.

00:23:18.360 --> 00:23:22.200
I believe the Lord has shown me this.

00:23:22.200 --> 00:23:28.171
But just because I'm flesh, just like anybody, we all can miss it.

00:23:28.171 --> 00:23:33.433
We all come short of the glory of God.

00:23:33.433 --> 00:23:35.433
Everybody has issues.

00:23:57.480 --> 00:23:57.695
And I could be off on a bad day because I had some bad pizza.

00:23:57.695 --> 00:24:11.895
I'm telling you these things, but when it comes to financial stuff, you need to take it to God in prayer and ask the Holy Spirit what he tells you to do.

00:24:11.895 --> 00:24:22.840
Whatever he tells you to do, do it.

00:24:22.840 --> 00:24:27.720
But I can tell you what I see in the visions.

00:24:30.360 --> 00:24:34.069
I see the five pillars, things like that.

00:24:34.069 --> 00:24:43.775
But what I really try to do is bring bait to bring you here to tell you that Jesus Christ is coming.

00:24:43.775 --> 00:24:46.628
You want to know about crypto?

00:24:46.628 --> 00:24:57.280
My heart is to tell you that you don't want to go to hell.

00:24:57.280 --> 00:25:01.010
You're running out of time.

00:25:13.240 --> 00:25:17.200
You want to fill your pockets, but you can't take it with you.

00:25:17.200 --> 00:25:20.320
There's a plague coming, ladies and gentlemen.

00:25:20.320 --> 00:25:26.160
There is an enemy that has infiltrated our nation because of the Biden administration.

00:25:26.160 --> 00:25:29.138
There are many terrorists in this nation.

00:25:33.030 --> 00:25:33.140
All those flies need to die.

00:25:33.140 --> 00:25:35.016
I had a bug zapper.

00:25:35.016 --> 00:25:44.040
There are enemies that have flooded our nation because we had open borders for four years of a Biden administration.

00:25:44.040 --> 00:25:45.924
Millions of people crossed over illegally.

00:25:45.924 --> 00:26:04.536
But many of them were a Trojan horse that came in here, and they could not get us, the Lord said, through a D-Day like it was in World War II when we invaded Germany.

00:26:35.840 --> 00:26:36.360
So they infiltrated through our borders, through the north and the south.

00:26:36.360 --> 00:26:41.568
I can even tell you where they crossed in; I can show you deep down.

00:26:43.260 --> 00:26:44.238
I know where they came in by Michigan.

00:26:51.840 --> 00:26:55.629
I saw a group of ten men come across the border of Michigan.

00:26:55.629 --> 00:27:00.280
I can tell you what they were wearing.

00:27:00.280 --> 00:27:05.753
I can tell you what they were driving.

00:27:26.955 --> 00:27:27.210
I don't know their license plate number, but I saw it deep.

00:27:33.320 --> 00:27:37.060
I even know the crossing points, and that was for us to pray over.

00:27:37.060 --> 00:27:38.276
It's not all glory.

00:27:38.276 --> 00:27:40.112
It's not anything about Brandon.

00:27:52.977 --> 00:27:53.354
But I try to bring these things to you all because I have such an urgency every time I do these videos.

00:27:53.354 --> 00:27:57.130
Even tonight I was like, "Do I do it?

00:28:05.493 --> 00:28:06.040
" I was like, "Man, it's late.

00:28:19.120 --> 00:28:19.560
